                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </li>

                    <li>
                        <a class="opener" href="#">How long does it take for a payment to be deposited ?<i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i></a>
                        <div class="slide js-acc-hidden">
                            <p>
                                Funds will typically be deposited into the Payee's banking account 3-5 business days after we begin processing the payment. This usually depends on your own bank. 
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </li>

                    <li>
                        <a class="opener" href="#">What are the services offered ? <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i></a>
