                            <p>
                               Yes, we have a separate account just for landlords who do not directly manage their property. Easily provide payments to the landlord by having them sign up for an account at no cost. If you are a landlord who manages your property yourself, sign up for a Property Manager account and take advantage of all of our services. 
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </li>

